description: Updates properties of a wireless gateway.

parameters.name: Id
parameters.description: The ID of the resource to update.

parameters.name: JoinEuiFilters
parameters.description: A list of JoinEuiRange used by LoRa gateways to filter LoRa frames. (list) --- A pair of join EUI describing a range [BegEui, EndEui], both ends are inclusive. (string) ---

parameters.name: NetIdFilters
parameters.description: A list of NetId values that are used by LoRa gateways to filter the uplink frames. (string) --- LoRaWAN network ID.
